{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-programs-js","path":"/programs/single-sign-on-sso-via-saml.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>HackerOne supports Single Sign-On (SSO) through Security Assertion Markup Language 2.0 (SAML 2.0) for these providers:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/programs/google-sso-saml-setup.html\">Google</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/programs/okta-sso-saml-setup.html\">Okta</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/programs/onelogin-sso-saml-setup.html\">OneLogin</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://support.bitium.com/administration/saml-hackerone/\">Bitium</a></li>\n<li>Centrify</li>\n<li>MS ADFS</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://azuremarketplace.microsoft.com/en-us/marketplace/apps/aad.hackerone\">Azure Active Directory</a></li>\n<li>Ping Identity</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://duo.com/docs/hackerone\">Duo</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://support.jumpcloud.com/support/s/article/single-sign-on-sso-with-hackerone2\">JumpCloud</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://support.hackerone.com/hc/en-us/requests/new\">Contact HackerOne</a> if you have another SAML provider.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><i>Note: Your program must be launched and not in sandbox mode to set up SAML.</i></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"set-up\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#set-up\" aria-label=\"set up permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Set Up</h3>\n<p>To configure Single Sign-On via SAML:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to <strong>Program Settings > General > Authentication</strong>.</li>\n<li>Click <strong>Setup SAML</strong> in the <em>Single Sign-on with SAML</em> section.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"saml setup\"\n        title=\"saml setup\"\n        src=\"/static/9fe7e248fb6834324656b697c2555720/0b533/saml-daisy-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9fe7e248fb6834324656b697c2555720/fac75/saml-daisy-1.png 125w,\n/static/9fe7e248fb6834324656b697c2555720/63868/saml-daisy-1.png 250w,\n/static/9fe7e248fb6834324656b697c2555720/0b533/saml-daisy-1.png 500w,\n/static/9fe7e248fb6834324656b697c2555720/1d69c/saml-daisy-1.png 750w,\n/static/9fe7e248fb6834324656b697c2555720/00d43/saml-daisy-1.png 1000w,\n/static/9fe7e248fb6834324656b697c2555720/a8979/saml-daisy-1.png 1828w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>Click <strong>Enter Configuration</strong> on the <em>SAML Configuration</em> page.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 25.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Image?\"\n        title=\"Image?\"\n        src=\"/static/f2b601b58a5dfb933c6875ded7b78556/0b533/saml-daisy-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f2b601b58a5dfb933c6875ded7b78556/fac75/saml-daisy-2.png 125w,\n/static/f2b601b58a5dfb933c6875ded7b78556/63868/saml-daisy-2.png 250w,\n/static/f2b601b58a5dfb933c6875ded7b78556/0b533/saml-daisy-2.png 500w,\n/static/f2b601b58a5dfb933c6875ded7b78556/1d69c/saml-daisy-2.png 750w,\n/static/f2b601b58a5dfb933c6875ded7b78556/00d43/saml-daisy-2.png 1000w,\n/static/f2b601b58a5dfb933c6875ded7b78556/53639/saml-daisy-2.png 1358w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>Enter information for these fields:</li>\n</ol>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Field</th>\n<th>Details</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Domain</td>\n<td>The  domain for users that will be required to use SAML authentication. The domain must be verified before entering. If you don't have a verified domain, see <a href=\"domain-verification.html\">Domain Verification</a> to set up a verified domain.  <em>Note: Please use your own domain, not the HackerOne domain.</em></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Single Sign On URL</td>\n<td>The URL from your SAML provider to initiate a single sign-on attempt, sometimes called the login URL.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>X509 Certificate</td>\n<td>The certificate from your SAML provider to verify the single sign-on response.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 129.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"setup SAML Configuration modal\"\n        title=\"setup SAML Configuration modal\"\n        src=\"/static/92185c94a297f598da7f04a45c3f358e/0b533/saml-daisy-3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/92185c94a297f598da7f04a45c3f358e/fac75/saml-daisy-3.png 125w,\n/static/92185c94a297f598da7f04a45c3f358e/63868/saml-daisy-3.png 250w,\n/static/92185c94a297f598da7f04a45c3f358e/0b533/saml-daisy-3.png 500w,\n/static/92185c94a297f598da7f04a45c3f358e/1d69c/saml-daisy-3.png 750w,\n/static/92185c94a297f598da7f04a45c3f358e/00d43/saml-daisy-3.png 1000w,\n/static/92185c94a297f598da7f04a45c3f358e/b67f3/saml-daisy-3.png 1338w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li>Click <strong>Save</strong>.</li>\n<li>Click <strong>Start Test</strong> in the <em>Test it</em> section of the SAML Configuration page.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 25.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Start Test button\"\n        title=\"Start Test button\"\n        src=\"/static/3c46a965a9929e60bc432c31d8ce9c1b/0b533/saml-daisy-4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3c46a965a9929e60bc432c31d8ce9c1b/fac75/saml-daisy-4.png 125w,\n/static/3c46a965a9929e60bc432c31d8ce9c1b/63868/saml-daisy-4.png 250w,\n/static/3c46a965a9929e60bc432c31d8ce9c1b/0b533/saml-daisy-4.png 500w,\n/static/3c46a965a9929e60bc432c31d8ce9c1b/1d69c/saml-daisy-4.png 750w,\n/static/3c46a965a9929e60bc432c31d8ce9c1b/00d43/saml-daisy-4.png 1000w,\n/static/3c46a965a9929e60bc432c31d8ce9c1b/b88bf/saml-daisy-4.png 1702w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"7\">\n<li>Click <strong>Run test</strong> in the <em>SAML Settings Test</em> modal that pops up.</li>\n<li>Click <strong>Start test now</strong>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 97.60000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"SAML start test\"\n        title=\"SAML start test\"\n        src=\"/static/837536b49d9d7f7375b57c22f880d429/0b533/saml-start-test.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/837536b49d9d7f7375b57c22f880d429/fac75/saml-start-test.png 125w,\n/static/837536b49d9d7f7375b57c22f880d429/63868/saml-start-test.png 250w,\n/static/837536b49d9d7f7375b57c22f880d429/0b533/saml-start-test.png 500w,\n/static/837536b49d9d7f7375b57c22f880d429/1d69c/saml-start-test.png 750w,\n/static/837536b49d9d7f7375b57c22f880d429/5b481/saml-start-test.png 846w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"9\">\n<li>Enter your login credentials to the test window. After your login attempt, the test will either succeed or fail and provide warning messages about your test login. If your test fails, run another test by going back to step 6 above.</li>\n<li>Click <strong>Verify Settings</strong>.  </li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 23.2%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Verify Settings\"\n        title=\"Verify Settings\"\n        src=\"/static/a19f8c8486bbc0b1fdd8884ea369db68/0b533/saml-daisy-verify-settings.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a19f8c8486bbc0b1fdd8884ea369db68/fac75/saml-daisy-verify-settings.png 125w,\n/static/a19f8c8486bbc0b1fdd8884ea369db68/63868/saml-daisy-verify-settings.png 250w,\n/static/a19f8c8486bbc0b1fdd8884ea369db68/0b533/saml-daisy-verify-settings.png 500w,\n/static/a19f8c8486bbc0b1fdd8884ea369db68/1d69c/saml-daisy-verify-settings.png 750w,\n/static/a19f8c8486bbc0b1fdd8884ea369db68/00d43/saml-daisy-verify-settings.png 1000w,\n/static/a19f8c8486bbc0b1fdd8884ea369db68/2af5b/saml-daisy-verify-settings.png 1697w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"11\">\n<li>Click <strong>Verify</strong> in the <em>Verify SAML Settings</em> modal. Once you verify your settings, you won't be able to change your settings or run tests on the domain anymore.</li>\n<li>Click <strong>Enable SAML</strong> once you're ready to migrate all user accounts to SAML authentication.</li>\n<li>Click <strong>Enable</strong> in the <em>Enable SAML</em> modal that pops up.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Once you've successfully enabled SAML, all users that are part of the domain will be required to authenticate using SAML. The passwords associated with those accounts will be removed. Users will receive instructions on their first log in informing them of the change.</p>\n<h3 id=\"additional-information\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#additional-information\" aria-label=\"additional information permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Additional Information</h3>\n<p>Here are some screenshots that provide additional details on Service Provider and Attribute mapping:</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 49.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"saml1\"\n        title=\"saml1\"\n        src=\"/static/8f3156293af7a8d1bf2e2a9e5d6e517f/0b533/saml-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8f3156293af7a8d1bf2e2a9e5d6e517f/fac75/saml-1.png 125w,\n/static/8f3156293af7a8d1bf2e2a9e5d6e517f/63868/saml-1.png 250w,\n/static/8f3156293af7a8d1bf2e2a9e5d6e517f/0b533/saml-1.png 500w,\n/static/8f3156293af7a8d1bf2e2a9e5d6e517f/1d69c/saml-1.png 750w,\n/static/8f3156293af7a8d1bf2e2a9e5d6e517f/00d43/saml-1.png 1000w,\n/static/8f3156293af7a8d1bf2e2a9e5d6e517f/2aa89/saml-1.png 1698w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50.4%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"saml_2\"\n        title=\"saml_2\"\n        src=\"/static/5463059e51b73a99c70af98744f6d0dc/0b533/saml-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5463059e51b73a99c70af98744f6d0dc/fac75/saml-2.png 125w,\n/static/5463059e51b73a99c70af98744f6d0dc/63868/saml-2.png 250w,\n/static/5463059e51b73a99c70af98744f6d0dc/0b533/saml-2.png 500w,\n/static/5463059e51b73a99c70af98744f6d0dc/1d69c/saml-2.png 750w,\n/static/5463059e51b73a99c70af98744f6d0dc/00d43/saml-2.png 1000w,\n/static/5463059e51b73a99c70af98744f6d0dc/bf286/saml-2.png 1688w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"configure-an-alternative-certificate\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#configure-an-alternative-certificate\" aria-label=\"configure an alternative certificate permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Configure an Alternative Certificate</h3>\n<p>If you need to switch your identity provider or if your current SAML certificate is expiring, you can configure an alternative SAML certificate to avoid having to disable your SSO integration during the update.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Only the admin of the program has the ability to configure the alternative certificate.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>To configure an alternative certificate:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to <strong>Program Settings > General > Authentication</strong>.</li>\n<li>Click <strong>configure</strong> next to <strong>X509 alternative certificate</strong>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Authentication settings page with SAML configured\"\n        title=\"Authentication settings page with SAML configured\"\n        src=\"/static/402c7d92023dd2341b2ea6d06c9fc8dd/0b533/alt-certificate-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/402c7d92023dd2341b2ea6d06c9fc8dd/fac75/alt-certificate-1.png 125w,\n/static/402c7d92023dd2341b2ea6d06c9fc8dd/63868/alt-certificate-1.png 250w,\n/static/402c7d92023dd2341b2ea6d06c9fc8dd/0b533/alt-certificate-1.png 500w,\n/static/402c7d92023dd2341b2ea6d06c9fc8dd/1d69c/alt-certificate-1.png 750w,\n/static/402c7d92023dd2341b2ea6d06c9fc8dd/00d43/alt-certificate-1.png 1000w,\n/static/402c7d92023dd2341b2ea6d06c9fc8dd/29beb/alt-certificate-1.png 1830w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>Enter the alternative certificate in the <strong>Configure alternative certificate</strong> window. </li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 92%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"configure alternative certificate modal \"\n        title=\"configure alternative certificate modal \"\n        src=\"/static/318948a2315ad25bb3eb4664468c44a0/0b533/alt-certificate-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/318948a2315ad25bb3eb4664468c44a0/fac75/alt-certificate-2.png 125w,\n/static/318948a2315ad25bb3eb4664468c44a0/63868/alt-certificate-2.png 250w,\n/static/318948a2315ad25bb3eb4664468c44a0/0b533/alt-certificate-2.png 500w,\n/static/318948a2315ad25bb3eb4664468c44a0/1d69c/alt-certificate-2.png 750w,\n/static/318948a2315ad25bb3eb4664468c44a0/00d43/alt-certificate-2.png 1000w,\n/static/318948a2315ad25bb3eb4664468c44a0/3d405/alt-certificate-2.png 1348w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>Click <strong>Save</strong>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>After the alternative certificate has been configured, users will be able to authenticate through the new SAML certificate.</p>\n<p>When the primary certificate isn't used anymore, you can promote the alternative certificate to the primary by clicking <strong>Promote alternative certificate to primary certificate</strong>. This will enable your primary certificate to be replaced with the alternative. </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 58.4%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"authentication settings page with alt certificate configured\"\n        title=\"authentication settings page with alt certificate configured\"\n        src=\"/static/8a75a2dca10e935c163b6420129b902d/0b533/alt-certificate-3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8a75a2dca10e935c163b6420129b902d/fac75/alt-certificate-3.png 125w,\n/static/8a75a2dca10e935c163b6420129b902d/63868/alt-certificate-3.png 250w,\n/static/8a75a2dca10e935c163b6420129b902d/0b533/alt-certificate-3.png 500w,\n/static/8a75a2dca10e935c163b6420129b902d/1d69c/alt-certificate-3.png 750w,\n/static/8a75a2dca10e935c163b6420129b902d/00d43/alt-certificate-3.png 1000w,\n/static/8a75a2dca10e935c163b6420129b902d/bcec6/alt-certificate-3.png 1834w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>","frontmatter":{"path":"/programs/single-sign-on-sso-via-saml.html","id":"programs/single-sign-on-sso-via-saml","title":"Single Sign-On (SSO) via SAML","description":null},"headings":[{"value":"Set Up"},{"value":"Additional Information"},{"value":"Configure an Alternative Certificate"}]}},"pageContext":{}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}